.name
BlitDemons
.author
Walter Strickler 
.version
1.0
.source
Includes source in C.
.description
This program implements the Demons cellular automaton as described in the
August, 1989, issue of Scientific American.  Using extremely simple rules
it exhibits rather complex behaviour.  Uses the blitter to perform over
350,000 cellgenerations per second.  
